Package: EPASnowModel
Type: Package
Title: EPA Snow Model
Version: 3.1.0
Author: Hyung Eum
Maintainer: Hyung Eum <hyung.eum@gov.ab.ca>
Description: Process based snow models (PBSM) with two variables or seven variables (daily and subdaily)
    Six snow models with daily data: Original PBSM, PBSM with S-curve, PBSM with S-curve and sublimation, 
	PBSM with 7 variables, PBSM with 7 variables and surface sublilmation and PBSM with 7 variables and surface/blowing sublilmation
	A snow model with subdaily data: PBSM_EPA with 6 subdaily meteorological variables
